Add `mask` parameter to attention calls in encoder and decoder layers
* **Encoder and Decoder Changes** - Add `mask` parameter to `MultiHeadAttention` call for self-attention in `EncoderLayer` class - Add `mask` parameter to `MultiHeadAttention` call for self-attention and cross attention in `DecoderLayer` class - Add `mask` parameter to `__call__` method for both encoder and decoder calls in `TransformerBase` class
* **Test Changes** - Add test cases to verify `mask` parameter in `MultiHeadAttention` calls for self-attention and cross attention in `DecoderLayer` class - Add test cases to verify `mask` parameter in `MultiHeadAttention` calls for self-attention in `EncoderLayer` class - Ensure `test_transformer_base` function initializes and tests the model with appropriate parameters and inputs, including `mask` parameter

Remove version constraints for dependencies in `requirements.txt`
* Remove version constraints for `flax`, `jax`, `pytest`, `transformers`, `datasets`, `numpy`, `scipy`, `torch`, `tensorflow`, and `tqdm`

Implement dynamic positional encoding and update requirements
* Modify `VishwamAI_Transformer/models/positional_encoding.py` to add a print statement for module test. * Update `requirements.txt` to include necessary dependencies for the project. - Add `flax`, `jax`, `pytest`, `transformers`, `datasets`, `numpy`, `scipy`, `torch`, `tensorflow`, and `tqdm`.

Implement advanced transformer features
Implement dynamic positional encoding, multi-perspective attention, and sparse/axial attention mechanisms in the VishwamAI transformers.
* **Dynamic Positional Encoding:** - Add `DynamicPositionalEncoding` class in `VishwamAI_Transformer/models/positional_encoding.py`. - Modify `PositionalEncoding` class to use the new dynamic encoding.
* **Encoder and Decoder Enhancements:** - Add multi-perspective attention and sparse/axial attention mechanisms to `EncoderLayer` and `DecoderLayer` classes in `VishwamAI_Transformer/models/encoder.py` and `VishwamAI_Transformer/models/decoder.py`.
* **Attention Mechanisms:** - Implement `MultiPerspectiveAttention` and `SparseAxialAttention` classes in `VishwamAI_Transformer/models/attention_mechanisms.py`.
* **Search Engine Integration:** - Implement real-time search query generation in `VishwamAI_Transformer/search_engine/query_generator.py`. - Implement multi-source information retrieval in `VishwamAI_Transformer/search_engine/multi_source_retriever.py`. - Implement contextual information scoring in `VishwamAI_Transformer/search_engine/information_scorer.py`. - Implement dynamic knowledge injection in `VishwamAI_Transformer/search_engine/knowledge_injector.py`.
* **Testing:** - Add test cases for `DynamicPositionalEncoding` in `tests/test_models/test_dynamic_positional_encoding.py`. - Add test cases for multi-perspective attention and sparse/axial attention mechanisms in `EncoderLayer` in `tests/test_models/test_encoder.py`.
